WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.940
=Episode 35=

01:39.540 --> 01:40.380
Mother.

01:40.490 --> 01:41.330
Impossible.

01:41.490 --> 01:42.980
Father would never use me to practice.

01:43.330 --> 01:44.330
He's my father.

01:45.330 --> 01:46.180
It's Cai Zhao's fault.

01:46.690 --> 01:47.590
She's talking nonsense.

01:47.600 --> 01:48.540
Let's just ignore her.

01:49.820 --> 01:51.690
Your grandfather once said

01:52.520 --> 01:54.210
he couldn't bear to part with his daughter.

01:54.900 --> 01:55.740
So,

01:56.570 --> 01:58.100
he'd never become the greatest.

01:59.930 --> 02:01.290
So that's why.

02:08.730 --> 02:09.570
Zhao.

02:09.730 --> 02:10.820
I'm begging you.

02:11.540 --> 02:13.610
You must protect Lingbo.

02:14.820 --> 02:16.010
Take her to Luoying Valley,

02:16.790 --> 02:17.900
or even to the demonic sect.

02:19.340 --> 02:20.780
Anywhere.

02:24.850 --> 02:26.850
Just keep her safe.

02:29.100 --> 02:30.820
I'm begging you.

02:30.820 --> 02:31.660
Mother.

02:32.130 --> 02:32.970
Lady Yin.

02:43.220 --> 02:44.130
Mother.

02:45.100 --> 02:46.130
Lingbo, be good.

02:48.130 --> 02:49.820
Go hide for a while.

02:50.410 --> 02:51.890
Wait for this to pass.

02:52.540 --> 02:53.380
It'll be fine.

02:54.850 --> 02:55.780
Mother.

02:59.010 --> 03:00.410
What's happening to you?

03:02.690 --> 03:03.530
I'm not leaving.

03:04.220 --> 03:05.730
I'm not going anywhere.

03:08.380 --> 03:09.890
Don't frighten me.

03:10.410 --> 03:11.250
Mother.

03:12.410 --> 03:13.250
Lady Yin.

03:14.690 --> 03:16.660
The Qingque Sect is on high alert.

03:17.980 --> 03:19.540
If Lingbo hadn't helped me,

03:20.340 --> 03:21.660
I couldn't have entered here.

03:24.010 --> 03:26.410
Please tell me where the secret passage is.

03:28.220 --> 03:29.340
I'll get Lingbo out safely.

03:33.980 --> 03:34.820
Come with me.

03:39.820 --> 03:40.660
Madam.

03:40.850 --> 03:41.780
Lord Qi is here.

04:07.340 --> 04:08.180
Yunke.

04:09.500 --> 04:11.540
Aren't you busy with the demon sect?

04:11.980 --> 04:13.130
Why come here then?

04:13.940 --> 04:14.780
Where's Lingbo?

04:15.340 --> 04:17.900
Isn't she in her room?

04:21.220 --> 04:22.220
Zhao has been here?

04:22.730 --> 04:23.570
Zhao?

04:25.140 --> 04:26.220
I don't know what you mean.

04:26.730 --> 04:27.900
Since you know,

04:28.810 --> 04:29.900
I won't explain further.

04:30.700 --> 04:31.540
Bring Lingbo out.

04:32.020 --> 04:33.050
She'll be willing

04:33.490 --> 04:34.580
to help her father

04:34.860 --> 04:35.980
fulfill his great ambition.

04:38.100 --> 04:38.940
Qi Yunke.

04:39.540 --> 04:41.610
How dare you call yourself her father?

04:41.610 --> 04:43.050
How could you be so heartless?

04:43.050 --> 04:44.850
Lingbo is your flesh and blood.

04:45.220 --> 04:46.980
Seems Zhao came here.

04:47.570 --> 04:48.820
Wenxun, there's a passage.

04:48.840 --> 04:49.620
Go and stop them.

04:53.850 --> 04:54.850
You must not go.

04:56.370 --> 04:57.210
Keep an eye on her.

04:57.340 --> 04:58.180
Lady Yin.

04:58.490 --> 04:59.370
At this point,

04:59.700 --> 05:00.850
you should heed the master.

05:05.810 --> 05:06.650
Dalou.

05:07.220 --> 05:08.060
The one

05:09.020 --> 05:11.100
you cherish most is Lingbo.

05:11.980 --> 05:13.580
Now they want Lingbo dead.

05:13.580 --> 05:14.780
Stop them at once.

05:14.780 --> 05:16.290
Stop them.

05:21.570 --> 05:22.410
Qi Yunke.

05:22.410 --> 05:23.610
Have you lost your mind?

05:24.220 --> 05:25.780
Lingbo carries your bloodline.

05:25.780 --> 05:27.580
She's also Yin family's blood.

05:28.490 --> 05:29.330
She can only

05:30.410 --> 05:31.980
blame her bad fate

05:32.410 --> 05:34.220
to be Yin Dai's granddaughter.

05:34.610 --> 05:36.730
You hate my father that much?

05:37.290 --> 05:38.490
Of course I do.

05:39.980 --> 05:41.040
Let me tell you the truth.

05:42.250 --> 05:44.410
Back then, I revealed his whereabouts

05:44.410 --> 05:46.370
to Zhao Tianba and Han Yisu.

05:47.020 --> 05:47.860
It was also me

05:48.220 --> 05:50.220
who drugged his guards.

05:50.220 --> 05:51.980
So in the fierce battle,

05:51.980 --> 05:53.140
they lost their strength.

05:53.580 --> 05:54.850
Qi Yunke!

06:04.260 --> 06:05.180
No one in the passage.

06:12.100 --> 06:13.020
Where did they go?

06:15.850 --> 06:17.250
Give it up.

06:18.290 --> 06:20.370
You'll never find them.

06:42.250 --> 06:43.090
My dear.

06:43.340 --> 06:44.700
Security is tight here.

06:45.140 --> 06:46.290
Where are you going?

06:55.580 --> 06:56.810
Madam, run!

07:00.050 --> 07:00.890
Nanny.

07:01.410 --> 07:02.250
Nanny!

07:04.050 --> 07:04.930
Nanny.

07:05.610 --> 07:06.780
Nanny.

07:09.370 --> 07:11.020
Run.

07:19.250 --> 07:20.090
Sulian.

07:21.730 --> 07:23.370
If you go back quietly,

07:24.290 --> 07:25.410
you can still be

07:25.410 --> 07:27.410
the honored Lady of Qingque Sect.

07:28.580 --> 07:29.540
Why?

07:31.810 --> 07:33.290
Why are you doing this to me?

07:47.850 --> 07:48.930
Qi Yunke.

07:50.610 --> 07:52.610
Do I mean nothing

07:52.610 --> 07:54.610
to you at all?

07:57.490 --> 07:59.700
I remember the first time I met you.

08:00.340 --> 08:01.370
You came down the mountain

08:02.580 --> 08:05.850
to give money and food to the poor.

08:06.250 --> 08:08.050
Back then, I thought,

08:09.700 --> 08:11.900
I was looking at a fairy.

08:13.020 --> 08:13.980
Your father was

08:13.980 --> 08:17.050
the greatest hero under heaven.

08:17.050 --> 08:17.890
I was just

08:19.400 --> 08:20.250
an ignorant boy

08:20.250 --> 08:22.850
from a poor widow's family.

08:23.860 --> 08:24.700
When your father

08:24.700 --> 08:26.490
wanted to take me as his disciple,

08:27.100 --> 08:28.900
Pingshu did have concerns.

08:28.900 --> 08:30.660
But I couldn't afford to think so much.

08:31.980 --> 08:34.420
To study under the master I adore,

08:34.420 --> 08:36.700
to be near the fairy in my heart...

08:36.700 --> 08:38.220
these were things an ignorant boy

08:38.220 --> 08:40.650
could only dream of.

08:41.850 --> 08:42.690
But the dream

08:43.370 --> 08:44.820
ended all too soon.

08:47.730 --> 08:49.490
That so-called greatest hero

08:50.340 --> 08:52.340
was nothing but a vile man.

08:52.980 --> 08:54.250
And you, the fairy,

08:54.610 --> 08:56.820
were nothing but narrow, shallow,

08:56.820 --> 08:58.650
and greedy.

09:02.220 --> 09:03.770
Your father told me

09:04.890 --> 09:08.220
a sect leader can't rely
only on righteousness.

09:08.940 --> 09:10.890
One hand in light, one cloaked in shade.

09:11.420 --> 09:14.060
Only then can you control everything.

09:14.060 --> 09:15.610
And so, like him,

09:15.610 --> 09:17.850
I bred countless shadow guards
and death-sworn.

09:19.060 --> 09:19.980
And you...

09:21.010 --> 09:22.610
When I decided to go to Mount Tu

09:23.100 --> 09:24.820
to help Pingshu,

09:24.820 --> 09:26.490
you brought me that cup of tea.

09:27.340 --> 09:28.580
It kept me asleep

09:29.610 --> 09:31.700
for six whole hours.

09:32.420 --> 09:33.260
And because of that,

09:34.060 --> 09:35.340
Pingshu returned gravely wounded.

09:35.650 --> 09:37.420
If you cared so deeply for Cai Pingshu,

09:37.980 --> 09:39.490
why didn't you marry her?

09:40.100 --> 09:41.370
Why did you marry me?

09:41.890 --> 09:42.980
You vulgar woman.

09:43.980 --> 09:45.820
You only have such petty thoughts.

09:47.420 --> 09:48.340
In your heart,

09:48.940 --> 09:51.300
there's nothing but affairs
between men and women.

09:52.340 --> 09:53.820
But Pingshu and I were different.

09:55.100 --> 09:55.940
She and I

09:56.650 --> 09:58.420
swore before the gods

09:58.420 --> 10:00.130
to be righteous heroes.

10:01.300 --> 10:02.940
For the people of the world,

10:02.940 --> 10:04.100
to help the suffering,

10:04.100 --> 10:05.650
to turn the tide of chaos,

10:05.650 --> 10:06.710
to uphold justice,

10:06.730 --> 10:08.200
to punish the wicked and aid the weak.

10:08.220 --> 10:09.400
So every grievance is answered

10:09.430 --> 10:10.980
and everyone can make their mark.

10:10.980 --> 10:12.130
With chivalry in our hearts,

10:12.130 --> 10:13.250
to drive away evil.

10:13.250 --> 10:14.180
Enough.

10:15.490 --> 10:17.980
If Cai Pingshu knew what you've done,

10:17.980 --> 10:19.530
she would never forgive you.

10:23.890 --> 10:25.100
Pingshu!

10:46.370 --> 10:47.980
But she is gone.

10:49.850 --> 10:50.700
And I

10:52.370 --> 10:53.700
died long ago.

10:55.250 --> 10:56.820
All thanks to your father

10:56.820 --> 10:58.010
and your sister,

10:58.730 --> 11:00.700
plotting step by step.

11:11.100 --> 11:12.250
How ridiculous.

11:13.730 --> 11:16.370
Are you any different from my father now?

11:17.010 --> 11:18.940
All for your own desire,

11:19.340 --> 11:20.890
without caring who dies.

11:22.940 --> 11:25.010
You're exactly the same.

11:32.420 --> 11:33.260
Mother.

11:33.820 --> 11:34.660
Mother.

11:39.130 --> 11:40.180
I only regret

11:41.060 --> 11:42.890
that my skills were lacking.

11:43.890 --> 11:45.650
I couldn't avenge

11:46.340 --> 11:47.580
my father.

11:49.300 --> 11:50.250
Didn't expect

11:51.530 --> 11:53.300
you to have some backbone.

11:55.610 --> 11:57.300
I'll ask you one last time.

11:57.300 --> 11:58.700
Where is Lingbo?

12:03.980 --> 12:04.820
Fine.

12:25.220 --> 12:27.420
Mother.

12:28.980 --> 12:32.060
Mother.

13:35.420 --> 13:36.420
Spread the word.

13:38.530 --> 13:41.650
Demonic rebels
infiltrated Double Lotus Palace.

13:42.770 --> 13:44.650
My wife and daughter

13:46.820 --> 13:48.100
were both killed.

13:49.250 --> 13:50.090
Yes.

14:23.850 --> 14:24.700
Lady Yin.

14:37.700 --> 14:38.610
Lingbo.

14:46.610 --> 14:48.180
I must avenge my mother.

14:48.180 --> 14:49.730
- Lingbo.
- Let go.

14:49.730 --> 14:51.250
I must avenge my mother.

14:52.940 --> 14:54.100
Your mother died saving you.

14:54.570 --> 14:55.770
Do you want her to die in vain?

14:56.230 --> 14:57.850
Let's find a way down the mountain first.

15:16.650 --> 15:17.770
I'll hold them off.

15:17.770 --> 15:18.850
Find somewhere to hide.

15:18.850 --> 15:20.340
When Xingjia sees we didn't return,

15:20.340 --> 15:21.610
he'll alert the others.

15:21.610 --> 15:22.530
You can come out then.

15:22.530 --> 15:23.370
No.

16:00.850 --> 16:01.980
Everyone stop!

16:08.130 --> 16:09.180
Li Wenxun.

16:09.580 --> 16:12.130
Qi Yunke need me alive

16:12.130 --> 16:14.180
to practice the Ziwei Method, right?

16:14.700 --> 16:15.820
Let Cai Zhao go.

16:16.370 --> 16:18.130
Or I'll die right here.

16:18.650 --> 16:19.980
Qi Yunke will never

16:19.980 --> 16:21.370
master the Ziwei Method.

16:21.370 --> 16:22.580
No, Lingbo.

16:24.730 --> 16:25.570
Cai Zhao.

16:26.100 --> 16:27.420
I'm your senior.

16:27.730 --> 16:29.650
Why do you always play the hero?

16:30.340 --> 16:32.060
This time it's my turn.

16:37.180 --> 16:38.300
Go.

16:50.890 --> 16:52.940
Take her back. Lord Qi's training matters.

17:19.940 --> 17:21.330
You're exhausted and drained.

17:21.860 --> 17:23.290
Take the top gold pill.

17:43.290 --> 17:44.220
Uncle Lei.

17:46.620 --> 17:49.010
You knew what Master was doing,

17:49.860 --> 17:50.700
didn't you?

17:51.980 --> 17:52.980
Does it matter

17:53.380 --> 17:54.290
whether I knew?

17:54.700 --> 17:57.090
The Qingque Sect belongs
to your master now.

17:58.380 --> 17:59.660
What can we do?

18:01.010 --> 18:02.290
Do you think

18:03.010 --> 18:04.380
Master is right?

18:04.380 --> 18:06.050
Don't you hate Yin Dai?

18:06.050 --> 18:08.090
Don't you want revenge for your aunt?

18:08.620 --> 18:09.940
Of course I hate Yin Dai.

18:20.490 --> 18:22.730
But this isn't the path of vengeance.

18:26.530 --> 18:27.700
Uncle Chang,

18:28.490 --> 18:29.810
Lord Song,

18:31.380 --> 18:32.380
Uncle Zhou,

18:33.860 --> 18:35.180
and Lingbo,

18:37.700 --> 18:39.090
what wrong have they done?

18:42.380 --> 18:43.290
It's too late now.

18:45.140 --> 18:46.250
Nothing can be undone.

18:54.530 --> 18:55.660
Stay here.

18:56.290 --> 18:57.380
He won't hurt you.

19:04.220 --> 19:05.060
Uncle Lei.

19:09.420 --> 19:11.140
Back then my aunt knew

19:11.810 --> 19:13.860
Nie Hengcheng had three years left.

19:15.180 --> 19:16.700
Mu Zhengyang told her.

19:19.380 --> 19:21.180
But she still went to Mount Tu.

19:22.490 --> 19:24.700
Even if she could save just one person,

19:26.250 --> 19:27.770
she'd go without hesitation.

19:28.180 --> 19:29.730
From start to end,

19:32.660 --> 19:34.290
she never regretted it.

19:36.010 --> 19:38.700
Even when bedridden later,

19:39.140 --> 19:42.140
even knowing Yin Dai used her,

19:42.980 --> 19:44.420
she never regretted it.

19:51.490 --> 19:52.770
She once told me,

19:56.250 --> 19:57.330
in this life,

20:00.380 --> 20:02.050
doing what you believe in

20:04.180 --> 20:05.620
is enough.

20:17.140 --> 20:18.050
Pingshu…

20:23.140 --> 20:24.980
My aunt needs no revenge.

20:24.980 --> 20:26.330
Nor does she need Master

20:26.330 --> 20:28.090
to slaughter in her name.

20:29.940 --> 20:30.900
What she wanted

20:36.050 --> 20:38.050
was a peaceful Jianghu.

20:42.620 --> 20:43.980
If she were alive,

20:49.220 --> 20:50.900
she would stop Master.

21:13.810 --> 21:15.420
Yuzhi's locked in the Discipline Hall.

21:16.250 --> 21:18.900
Dai Fengchi and the others,
the back mountain dungeon.

21:19.330 --> 21:20.770
The antidote to the softening powder.

21:23.220 --> 21:24.530
Go and free them.

21:46.940 --> 21:48.050
Thank you, Uncle Lei.

22:16.770 --> 22:17.700
Pingshu.

22:19.050 --> 22:20.320
This time,

22:21.210 --> 22:22.560
did I do the right thing?

22:24.220 --> 22:26.860
(Righteous Spirit)
In Jianghu, strength rules.

22:28.250 --> 22:29.660
But words mean nothing

22:30.250 --> 22:32.810
beside supreme power.

22:33.530 --> 22:34.570
As long as the three of us

22:34.980 --> 22:36.290
perfect our skills,

22:36.290 --> 22:37.980
we'll form a triangle of power

22:38.290 --> 22:40.140
and fear no one.

22:40.530 --> 22:41.370
Agreed.

22:42.250 --> 22:43.180
In that case,

22:43.620 --> 22:45.420
we'll guard you while you train.

22:45.940 --> 22:47.090
Once you succeed,

22:47.490 --> 22:49.570
share the secret with us.

22:49.900 --> 22:51.490
If you break your word,

22:52.180 --> 22:54.570
I'll give up the Guangtian Sect throne

22:54.570 --> 22:56.860
and expose you to the world.

23:00.620 --> 23:02.700
When Nie Hengcheng trained back then,

23:03.050 --> 23:04.660
he nearly went berserk.

23:05.090 --> 23:08.220
I merely wished to test it for you.

23:08.860 --> 23:09.940
Would that be acceptable?

23:14.380 --> 23:16.010
Lord Qi, train in peace.

23:16.010 --> 23:18.220
We will guard Fengyun Peak for you.

23:20.220 --> 23:21.250
I'm grateful to you both.

23:37.180 --> 23:38.020
You really trust him?

23:38.730 --> 23:40.530
At this point, what choice do we have?

23:41.330 --> 23:42.530
News has spread that I killed

23:42.860 --> 23:44.290
my father-in-law's family

23:44.290 --> 23:46.010
to make corpse slaves.

23:46.980 --> 23:48.220
If we don't go all in now,

23:48.220 --> 23:49.490
shall we wait to be judged?

23:52.940 --> 23:54.530
Song Shijun isn't dead yet.

23:54.900 --> 23:56.770
Your seat as Guangtian Sect leader

23:57.180 --> 23:58.700
may not be secure.

24:01.050 --> 24:01.980
Remove one more man,

24:03.140 --> 24:04.140
and it will be.

24:09.810 --> 24:10.860
Two fools.

24:11.770 --> 24:13.490
You're the leader of the six sects.

24:13.810 --> 24:15.570
Why raise two rivals?

24:15.570 --> 24:16.810
They're not fools.

24:17.620 --> 24:18.660
They're greedy.

24:18.660 --> 24:19.900
Greed

24:20.620 --> 24:21.980
blinds them.

24:24.770 --> 24:25.610
Dalou.

24:29.490 --> 24:30.330
What do you think?

24:34.770 --> 24:37.220
I was once an orphaned beggar,

24:37.220 --> 24:38.730
dying by the roadside.

24:40.010 --> 24:41.940
Master and Ms. Cai saved me.

24:41.940 --> 24:43.250
That is why I live today.

24:43.250 --> 24:44.700
Whatever Master does,

24:44.700 --> 24:46.860
I know it is for Ms. Cai.

24:46.860 --> 24:48.660
I'll serve you unto death.

24:58.050 --> 24:59.290
In this world,

25:00.420 --> 25:02.810
few still remember

25:03.730 --> 25:05.490
Pingshu's kindness.

25:09.810 --> 25:10.650
Yunke,

25:10.860 --> 25:12.140
Lingbo's in the secret chamber.

25:16.900 --> 25:18.900
(Righteous Spirit)

25:32.980 --> 25:34.530
Master sent you to kill me?

25:34.810 --> 25:36.490
Don't wrong Qi Yunke.

25:37.620 --> 25:38.620
Your master treats you

25:39.700 --> 25:41.730
like his own child.

25:42.730 --> 25:44.290
This place is so hidden.

25:44.900 --> 25:46.420
If I hadn't followed the food carrier,

25:46.810 --> 25:48.050
I'd never find it.

25:48.620 --> 25:50.330
He could abandon his own daughter,

25:51.620 --> 25:53.660
yet hides you like a treasure.

25:53.660 --> 25:54.500
Sadly,

25:55.810 --> 25:57.330
today's your last day.

26:04.730 --> 26:05.570
Brother.

26:06.220 --> 26:07.620
Do you hate me that much?

26:08.090 --> 26:09.220
Of course I do.

26:11.140 --> 26:13.250
I am the true heir of Guangtian Sect.

26:13.250 --> 26:15.490
Yet everyone only knows you.

26:17.420 --> 26:18.730
You deserve to die.

26:35.050 --> 26:35.890
Cai Zhao?

26:36.660 --> 26:37.530
You dare come here?

26:59.180 --> 27:00.020
Mu Qingyan?

27:00.700 --> 27:01.570
Why are you here?

27:03.700 --> 27:04.540
I protect my own.

27:05.490 --> 27:07.010
Someone hurt my Golden Peng.

27:07.010 --> 27:08.660
Of course I came to see why.

27:09.730 --> 27:10.700
Thank you, Mr. Mu.

27:11.140 --> 27:12.490
And last time at Xuankong Nunnery,

27:12.490 --> 27:14.420
thanks for saving Zhao.

27:14.420 --> 27:15.770
That was for Zhao.

27:16.290 --> 27:17.490
Why thank me, Song?

27:19.980 --> 27:21.490
Enough chatter.

27:21.810 --> 27:23.090
Master has captured Lingbo.

27:23.360 --> 27:25.360
He's about to finish
Ziwei Method's final layer.

27:25.620 --> 27:26.620
We must stop him.

27:27.570 --> 27:29.380
First we must find him.

27:29.700 --> 27:30.730
Where is Qi Yunke?

27:31.220 --> 27:32.940
Wouldn't you know best?

27:32.940 --> 27:34.220
The final layer

27:34.220 --> 27:35.810
is extremely dangerous.

27:36.330 --> 27:38.330
One mistake

27:39.250 --> 27:40.700
and he'll lose control.

27:40.700 --> 27:42.010
So the old tunnels

27:42.380 --> 27:44.140
and unstable chambers can't be used.

27:44.570 --> 27:46.140
He must choose

27:46.140 --> 27:48.050
a place unknown and secure.

27:48.270 --> 27:49.130
Yuzhi.

27:49.250 --> 27:50.570
Did Yin Dai have other chambers?

27:50.860 --> 27:52.140
Grandfather did have

27:52.140 --> 27:54.140
a forbidden training ground full of traps.

27:54.140 --> 27:54.990
Where?

27:55.000 --> 27:55.880
Dusk Palace.

27:56.290 --> 27:57.220
We split up.

27:57.900 --> 27:59.090
This is the antidote.

27:59.860 --> 28:01.730
Go free the imprisoned.

28:01.730 --> 28:03.370
Master's Ziwei Method is nearly complete.

28:03.980 --> 28:05.280
How can just two of you stop him?

28:05.280 --> 28:06.120
Let's go together.

28:06.120 --> 28:07.570
I'll keep Zhao safe.

28:08.140 --> 28:09.220
As for you, Song,

28:10.250 --> 28:11.860
you nearly became a corpse slave

28:12.330 --> 28:14.140
and almost died covering our retreat.

28:15.570 --> 28:16.410
Yuzhi.

28:17.140 --> 28:18.110
Saving them comes first.

28:19.570 --> 28:20.850
Zhao, let's go.

28:21.100 --> 28:22.570
Guanyue is waiting down there.

28:22.570 --> 28:23.700
If he grows impatient,

28:24.090 --> 28:25.700
he might attack the sect.

28:26.730 --> 28:27.570
You brought people?

28:28.380 --> 28:29.770
Do you think the Chief of Li Sect

28:30.180 --> 28:31.250
came alone?

28:41.050 --> 28:42.180
What a coincidence.

28:43.050 --> 28:44.220
Since everyone's here,

28:44.530 --> 28:45.900
let's go up together

28:46.220 --> 28:47.330
and take Fengyun Peak.

28:47.600 --> 28:48.950
Righteous and demonic cannot unite.

28:48.980 --> 28:49.980
Together? Impossible.

28:50.050 --> 28:52.250
Or do you seek to profit from chaos?

28:52.700 --> 28:53.900
Young Lord Zhou,

28:53.900 --> 28:54.980
Lord Zhou was killed

28:54.980 --> 28:56.730
by someone from the six sects.

28:56.730 --> 28:57.810
Young Master came

28:57.810 --> 28:59.120
to help you anyway.

28:59.900 --> 29:01.620
How can you be so blind?

29:01.620 --> 29:03.220
At a time like this,

29:03.220 --> 29:04.330
you're still arguing?

29:05.770 --> 29:06.610
Qi…

29:08.380 --> 29:09.220
Lord Qi

29:09.730 --> 29:10.860
has lost control.

29:11.530 --> 29:13.090
If not stopped in time,

29:13.090 --> 29:14.620
there will be more bloodshed.

29:15.290 --> 29:16.620
At a moment of right and wrong,

29:16.620 --> 29:18.140
both sides must set aside hatred

29:18.140 --> 29:19.170
and fight together.

29:19.330 --> 29:20.170
That's right.

29:20.290 --> 29:21.420
In urgent times, we adapt.

29:21.770 --> 29:23.220
Let's go up together.

29:23.810 --> 29:25.140
But heed my warning.

29:25.730 --> 29:28.050
Qingque Sect guards Beichen.

29:29.770 --> 29:31.180
Do not act rashly.

29:31.770 --> 29:32.980
With Young Master absent,

29:34.090 --> 29:36.330
we follow Luoying Valley's lead.

29:37.010 --> 29:38.290
Young Master must heed

29:39.180 --> 29:40.660
his father-in-law's words.

29:42.620 --> 29:44.010
Very well.

29:44.010 --> 29:44.900
Then let's go up.

29:47.530 --> 29:48.370
Why?

29:48.620 --> 29:49.730
It's Master?

29:49.730 --> 29:51.290
Master was blinded by hatred

29:51.940 --> 29:52.860
and lost his way.

29:54.940 --> 29:55.780
He…

29:56.800 --> 29:58.220
He wants to use Lingbo for training.

30:00.770 --> 30:02.330
Master will use Lingbo to train?

30:02.770 --> 30:03.610
Don't worry.

30:03.660 --> 30:05.490
Zhao and Mr. Mu have gone to save her.

30:06.810 --> 30:07.980
- Lingbo.
- Fengchi.

30:07.980 --> 30:08.820
Lingbo.

30:09.050 --> 30:10.610
- Fengchi.
- Fengchi.

30:19.710 --> 30:21.180
I'm also a disciple of Luoying Valley.

30:21.620 --> 30:23.420
My martial arts are poor,

30:23.420 --> 30:25.180
but training with milady

30:25.180 --> 30:26.330
gave me some inner strength.

30:26.860 --> 30:27.700
Ding,

30:28.010 --> 30:28.850
regulate your breath.

30:29.140 --> 30:30.460
The poison isn't gone yet.

30:30.480 --> 30:31.650
Circulate your qi to expel it.

30:34.620 --> 30:35.980
We have urgent matters now.

30:35.980 --> 30:36.900
We must split up.

30:38.050 --> 30:39.250
The others in the cell

30:39.570 --> 30:40.410
are counting on you.

30:42.080 --> 30:43.660
I must go to Thousandfold Cliff

30:43.660 --> 30:44.510
to release the chains

30:44.520 --> 30:45.430
and let them up.

30:45.900 --> 30:46.740
Wait.

30:49.570 --> 30:50.700
Things are urgent.

30:51.460 --> 30:52.370
I'll fight beside you.

30:52.920 --> 30:54.220
- Your injuries…
- Don't worry.

30:54.490 --> 30:55.410
Saving people

30:55.450 --> 30:56.670
is something I can help with.

30:57.490 --> 30:58.420
Leave it to me.

30:59.290 --> 31:00.220
Be careful.

31:20.860 --> 31:23.530
She was your wife for 20 years.

31:27.730 --> 31:29.250
Why did you kill her?

31:33.620 --> 31:35.570
Because she was Yin Dai's descendant.

31:41.420 --> 31:43.330
Will you kill me too?

31:58.220 --> 31:59.180
You are my daughter.

32:00.570 --> 32:01.620
I won't kill you.

32:02.770 --> 32:04.420
I only need your inner power

32:05.770 --> 32:07.220
to train.

32:08.290 --> 32:09.250
Father does this

32:10.220 --> 32:11.290
for your own good.

32:13.220 --> 32:14.900
Just borrowing my power?

32:15.860 --> 32:16.700
Yes.

32:17.050 --> 32:17.980
Your mother

32:18.980 --> 32:20.700
spoiled you before.

32:21.570 --> 32:22.700
From now on,

32:23.700 --> 32:25.290
I'll teach you himself

32:26.140 --> 32:27.530
and make you worthy.

32:29.220 --> 32:30.730
Don't you want to help me

32:31.730 --> 32:33.050
complete the great cause?

32:47.490 --> 32:48.380
Father.

32:54.180 --> 32:56.620
It's been long
since you spoke to me like this.

33:28.810 --> 33:29.940
Lord Qi's order.

33:29.940 --> 33:31.450
No one may go up the mountain.

33:36.770 --> 33:37.700
Zhuang.

33:37.700 --> 33:38.540
Let him in.

33:39.050 --> 33:39.890
Move aside.

33:42.010 --> 33:43.490
Zhuang, Lord Qi's Master was

33:43.510 --> 33:45.410
the Man in Black
who wiped out the Chang family.

33:45.440 --> 33:46.660
Your master

33:46.660 --> 33:48.220
and Uncle Li were their accomplices.

33:48.220 --> 33:49.730
We were all deceived.

33:49.730 --> 33:50.570
I know.

33:50.860 --> 33:51.770
You knew?

33:52.330 --> 33:53.530
And still helped the villain?

33:54.090 --> 33:54.930
Fan.

33:55.290 --> 33:57.250
I was a useless outer disciple.

33:58.330 --> 33:59.860
Master chose me for the inner sect.

34:00.180 --> 34:01.180
He taught me martial arts

34:01.530 --> 34:02.660
and entrusted me with duties.

34:03.810 --> 34:05.090
I cannot betray his grace.

34:14.860 --> 34:15.980
It must be Yuzhi.

34:17.570 --> 34:19.050
Follow us to Fengyun Peak!

34:19.050 --> 34:20.610
Charge!

34:59.090 --> 34:59.930
What's wrong?

35:00.940 --> 35:01.940
I won't stand here again

35:02.650 --> 35:04.340
watching you walk away.

35:07.820 --> 35:09.340
Mu Qingyan, you…

35:09.340 --> 35:10.930
It's fine. Saving her comes first.

35:12.780 --> 35:13.920
Your poison isn't fully gone.

35:13.940 --> 35:15.180
You can barely protect yourself.

35:15.190 --> 35:17.030
Besides, it's inside
the Six Sects of Beichen.

35:17.060 --> 35:18.210
Don't risk yourself.

35:18.210 --> 35:19.540
But I won't become Mu Zhengyang.

35:20.130 --> 35:21.050
I won't be like him,

35:21.650 --> 35:22.900
cutting off love

35:22.900 --> 35:24.130
for power and greed,

35:24.130 --> 35:26.130
and risking both our lives.

35:28.050 --> 35:28.890
Zhao.

35:29.260 --> 35:30.210
I won't let you follow

35:30.210 --> 35:31.650
your aunt's path.

35:34.740 --> 35:35.580
Come on.

35:37.720 --> 35:48.380
=Generation to Generation=

36:07.140 --> 36:11.550
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

36:12.115 --> 36:16.730
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

36:17.070 --> 36:21.635
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

36:22.160 --> 36:26.460
♪Free to wander in the world♪

36:29.405 --> 36:34.105
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

36:34.630 --> 36:38.920
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

36:39.580 --> 36:43.610
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

36:43.925 --> 36:49.050
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

36:49.625 --> 36:54.435
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

36:54.650 --> 36:58.820
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

36:59.545 --> 37:03.480
♪I freely roam in the world♪

37:03.980 --> 37:09.255
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

37:31.985 --> 37:37.115
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

37:37.480 --> 37:41.850
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

37:42.115 --> 37:46.245
♪I freely roam in the world♪

37:46.430 --> 37:52.005
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
